data.description: NEW ROOF COMING SOON!!! World's Largest 55+ Community in The Villages. Welcome to this charming home with its bright and airy open concept kitchen, living, family and dining room perfect for entertaining and spending time with family. Situated on a large corner lot (a gardener's dream), you'll immediately feel part of what The Villages is all about...community! Upon entering the home, you'll be greeted by cascading natural light from the wall of windows. This home also boasts ample storage and multi-use space perfect for the artist, crafter or hobbyist. The master bedroom has 2 closets, and an upgraded master bathroom with an oversized shower. There is updated flooring throughout the home. The tile in kitchen is warm and inviting. The new dishwasher has stainless steel interior and 3rd rack. The home has a covered carport with secured storage, attached laundry, a workshop and golf cart parking space, and a metal roof. There is irrigation for the gardens. This conveniently located home is a short golf cart ride to Orange Blossom Hills Country Club and its stunning rock waterfall pool, Spanish Springs shopping and dining. Your vacation living starts today!
